$INIT_BOITE
Local Char    OBJLIS(GLONAOB)(0..10), DESLIS(80)(0..10), BOX1(10)
Local Integer CHGLIS(0..10), BROLIS(0..10), TRELIS(0..10)
Local Char    SAIRAP(50)(1..16)
Local Integer DERLU , AFOLDEF
Local Char    ABRENA(GLONABR)
DERLU = 0
AFOLDEF = 1
ABRENA = ""
BOX1 = "GAU_CHE"
OBJLIS(0) = "TXW"
CHGLIS(0) = 2
BROLIS(0) = 2
TRELIS(0) = 2
DESLIS(0) = "LSTGRP+TXSNAM+VERSION"
If clalev([M:TXM0])=0 : Local Mask TXSM0 [TXM0] : Endif
If clalev([M:TXM1])=0 : Local Mask TXSM1 [TXM1] : Endif
If clalev([M:TXM2])=0 : Local Mask TXSM2 [TXM2] : Endif
If clalev([M:TXM3])=0 : Local Mask TXSM3 [TXM3] : Endif
Gosub TIT
nolign = 1
If clalev([F:ACC])=0 : Local File ACCES  [ACC] : Endif
If clalev([F:TXS])=0 : Local file TXSA [TXS] : Endif
If clalev([F:AXX1])=0 : Local file ATEXTRA [AXX1] : Endif
If clalev([F:AXX2])=0 : Local file ATEXTRA [AXX2] : Endif
Link [TXW] With
& [ACC]CODACC=GUSER;[F:TXW]ACS,
& [TXS]TXS1=[F:TXW]TXSNAM,
& [AXX1]AXX0="TXSA";"TXSDES";GLANGUE;[F:TXS]TXSNAM;"",
& [AXX2]AXX0="TXSA";"GRPDES";GLANGUE;[F:TXS]LSTGRP;""
& As [TXW_]
& Order By Key TXW0
Return

$DEF_BOITE
Gosub HORODAT From WGOTXW
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Inpbox "OTXW" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [TXM0]
&   Folder Mask [TXM1]
& , Folder Mask [TXM2]
& , Folder Mask [TXM3]
&  Treebox [TXW_] GAU_CHE
&   [F:TXS]LSTGRP-':'-[F:AXX2]TEXTE Using "" Titled TITSEL(1) ,
&   TXSNAM-':'-[F:AXX1]TEXTE Using "" Titled TITSEL(2) ,
&   VERSION-':'-VERDES
&   Titled ""
& As [TXM1]
Titled [TXM1] TIT
Return

$VISU_BOITE
Gosub INIT_BOITE
Gosub HORODAT From WGOTXW
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Inpbox "OTXW" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [TXM0]
&   Folder Mask [TXM1]
& , Folder Mask [TXM2]
& , Folder Mask [TXM3]
& As [TXM1]
Titled [TXM1] TIT
Gosub AFF_BOITE
Return

$AFF_BOITE
Boxact [TXM1] Folder AFOLDEF
Return

$SAISIE_BOITE
